filter(function, list) { 
    filtered-list = (); 
 
    for element in list { 
        if (function(element)) { 
            push(filtered-list, element); 
        } 
    } 
 
    return filtered-list; 
} 
 
greaterThanTwo(num) { 
    return num > 2; 
} 
 
#out { 
    numbers-greater-than-two: filter(greaterThanTwo, (1 2 3 4 5)) 
}
